metadata.name: Serene Morning
metadata.description:
Seeing crowded places empty with the company of a beautiful and calm morning is priceless. Seka Park in Kocaeli is one of the most crowded places on a sunny day or on weekends. It is an old paper factory by the Kocaeli Bay, turned into a museum now and its garden has been redesigned to be a park and recreational area.

The sea being so calm, almost like a mirror has been a great opportunity on that day.

This photograph is my contribution to the Loyalty Over Royalty #LOR event. 

Taken on January 2, 2019 at Kocaeli, Turkey.  
W/ FujiFilm XPro 2 Camera and XF10-24mmF4 R OIS lens  
5183x3456 px
